text: Kjellbjørg Lunde (born 26 November 1944 in Naustdal) is a Norwegian politician for the Socialist Left Party. ==Career== She was elected to the Norwegian Parliament from Hordaland in 1981, and was re-elected on three occasions. Lunde was a member of Stord municipality council in the periods 1975-1979 and 1979-1981\. ==References== * Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Socialist Left Party (Norway) politicians Category:Members of the Storting Category:People from Naustdal Category:20th-century Norwegian politicians
